name: SeattleTravelTimes
0:
”Alexa, ask Travel Time from Seattle to SeaTac.”
”Alexa, ask Travel Time from Renton to Bellevue.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: travel time
des:
Never get stuck again on the busy Seattle freeways sitting in traffic. Ask Alexa for "Travel Times"

Get live traffic information on current travel times between multiple locations around Seattle. Travel times between locations are provided by WSDOT based on live traffic conditions. 

To get started: Say "Alexa, ask Travel Time from Seattle to SeaTac" or "Alexa, Travel Time to Renton from Bellevue"

Sample Response: "Current travel time from Seattle to SeaTac is 18 min, 3 min more than the average travel time. Approximate distance is 14 miles."

"Alexa, ask Travel Time for supported locations."
Supported Locations:
Seattle
Bellevue 
Redmond 
Seatac 
Bothell 
Everett
Federal Way
Renton 
Lynnwood 
Woodinville
Issaquah 
Tacoma 
Arlington
Auburn
Southcenter
Marysville
Alderwood
